text: For modelling i use Zbrush and Maya, for texturing im quite reliant on Substance painter and then i tend to clean up any seams and and add finishing touches in Mari. I'm also getting stronger with nodal work in Maya so once ive finished my textures i tend to add a few more nodes with noise and such in maya. Right now i'm more focused on modelling and texturing however i've been told it would also be wise to start learning muscle sim.

Unfortunately i don't have a full showreel yet. I actually have a showreel deadline on monday and should have one put together by then to show you, however i do have som WIP snaps of the pieces with their concepts.
